{"tid":1717560,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史上冇一場仗係我地咁而打得贏！醒呀！","createTime":"2019-11-13T15:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T04:05:01.000Z","uid":147394,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fa9d9b784ab94138933ffd91422b99bb19d2722e","tid":1717560,"uid":147394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:44:14.000Z","msg":"有咩理由會話比對家知我地個陣係點，同時對方不用一分力而得到情報。<br />\n依家打陣地，警甴都要事先岀直升機睇下咩環境先諗點打。<br />\n我地中大邊度防守位置邊度攻擊位置，如果警甴要知道最低成本都要派鬼入黎，但依家自動由傳媒即時送比警甴，醒下啦大家，我知冇可能控制傳媒做啲咩，但大家諗下，傳媒職責做到對戰時既雙方行為已經足夠。<br />\n有冇可能逼傳媒岀返去某個位置？<br />\n<br />\n我明白大家對傳媒既敬意，我都一樣，但打仗唔應該有哩啲考慮，希望比個機會大家諗一諗哩樣野。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"7b12041dc372277f87e1da285233100a22f595a6","tid":1717560,"uid":73826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:47:14.000Z","msg":"呢個要推"},{"pid":"c9a11ad3756e64801802edb49abc75e78d5e7716","tid":1717560,"uid":73826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:47:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c1ac7a3b9cb0f619327096e9cb5608509f95d9d","tid":1717560,"uid":147394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:47:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af51bb1567c09aaceda183adbdb00a30c94300ee","tid":1717560,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:48:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"275385b51e704dabbd46d59855c18de62bc2f95f","tid":1717560,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e5c03757de29a1fefc8a770d621a1930270077","tid":1717560,"uid":73826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:48:31.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"f2aab514342a0f72073a40907e7a0c07e22a65d3","tid":1717560,"uid":147394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20